<td>Abandoned factory</td>
<td>Industrial hazards, toxic slime, and aerial enemies. Eggman's corruption spreads across the landscape</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Deep Sea Zone</strong></td>
<td>Flooded ruins</td>
<td>Underwater sections where Sonic must move fast (he can't swim). Features statue puzzles and eerie atmosphere</td>
</tr>
